Summary of interpolation errors

Im using the Eucledian Norm of the differences between the original function and the interpolation method. Specifically \[ || f(x)-q(x) ||^2 = \left[ \sum_i \left( f(x_i)-q(x_i) \right)^2 \right]^{\frac{1}{2}} \]
